# Mobile-first intake

- Layout: `max-w-md mx-auto`, large tap targets, `min-h-dvh` where appropriate.
- Wizard: debounced autosave (PATCH), localStorage backup, back navigation without wiping draft.
- Step 0: format hint + privacy line; staged parse spinner labels.
- Show save status chip (Saving… / Saved) on steps 1–3.
- Required fields validated before Next; native inputs with clear placeholders.

Match existing Tailwind patterns (`brand-600`, `field` class on intake page).
